quran[24{c,v,t}:
51,7,qasam hai mutafarraq shaklon walay aasman ki
51,8,( akhirat ke baray mein ) tumhari baat aik dosray se mukhtalif hai
51,9,uss se wohi bur-ghashta hota hai jo haq se phira howa hai
51,10,maaray gay qiyaas o gumaan se hukum laganay walay
51,11,jo jahalat mein ghark aur ghaflat mein madhosh hain
51,12,puchhte hain aakhir woh roz-e jaza kab aeye ga ?
51,13,woh uss roz aeye ga jab yeh log aag par tapay jayen ge
51,14,( inn se kaha jaye ga ) ab chako maza apne ftne ka yeh wohi cheez hai jis ke liye tum jaldi macha rahay thay
51,15,Albata mut-taqi log uss roz baghoon aur chashmon mein hon ge
51,16,jo kuch unn ka rab inhen day ga usay khusi khusi le rahay hon ge woh uss din ke anay se pehlay naiko car thay
51,17,raton ko kam hi sotay thay
51,18,phir wohi raat ke pichlle pahron mein maffi mangte thay
51,19,aur unn ke malon mein haq tha sayel aur mahroom ke liye
51,20,zameen mein bohat si nishanain hain yaqeen laane walon ke liye
51,21,aur khud tumahray apne wujood mein hain kya tum ko sujhta nahi ?
51,22,aasman hi mein hai tumhara rizaq bhi aur woh cheez bhi jis ka tum se wada kya ja raha hai
51,23,"pas qasam hai aasman aur zameen ke maalik ki, yeh baat haq hai, aisi hi yakeeni jaisay tum bol rahay ho"
51,24,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ibrahim ke Muaziz mehmanon ki hekiyaat bhi tumhe pohanchi hai ?"
51,25,"jab woh uss ke haan aeye to kaha aap ko salam hai uss ne kaha"" aap logon ko bhi salam hai kuch na aashna se log hain """
51,26,"phir woh chupkay se apne ghar walon ke paas gaya, aur aik mota taaza bitchrha laa kar"
51,27,mehmanon ke agay paish kya uss ne kaha aap hazraat khatay nahi ?
51,28,"phir woh apne dil mein un se dara unhon ne kaha daryay nahi, aur ussay aik Zee ilm larke ki paidaiesh ka Musda sunaya"
51,29,"yeh sun kar uss ki biwi chikhati hui agay barhi aur is ne apna mun pait liya aur kehnay lagi,"" boorhi, banjh! """
51,30,"unhon ne kaha"" yahi kuch farmaya hai tairay rab ne, woh hakeem hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai """
